    "whoUses": "Infectious disease specialists, pulmonologists, and neurologists typically diagnose and treat tuberculous neuritis, often in hospital or specialized TB clinic settings. This code commonly appears on EOBs for patients with disseminated TB who require imaging, nerve conduction studies, or specialist consultations to confirm nerve involvement.",
