    "whoUses": "Infectious disease specialists, rheumatologists, orthopedic surgeons, and pulmonologists use this code when diagnosing and managing TB infections in joints, typically during office visits, imaging studies, or surgical procedures. This code commonly appears on EOB statements for patients undergoing TB treatment, joint imaging, or orthopedic consultations related to suspected or confirmed tuberculous arthritis.",
