    "whoUses": "This code is used by pulmonologists, infectious disease specialists, and critical care physicians, typically in hospital settings (inpatient) or emergency departments when diagnosing and treating severe disseminated TB. It commonly appears on EOB statements for hospitalized patients, often accompanied by related charges for imaging, laboratory tests, and intensive monitoring.",
