    "whoUses": "Infectious disease specialists, neurologists, and emergency medicine physicians commonly diagnose and treat this condition in hospital settings, particularly in the ER or ICU. Internal medicine doctors and hospitalists also manage these patients. This code appears on EOB statements for hospitalized patients with confirmed Listeria infection of the central nervous system.",
