    "whoUses": "Infectious disease specialists, neurologists, and primary care physicians typically use this code when a patient with confirmed Lyme disease develops nervous system complications. It appears most commonly in outpatient neurology or infectious disease clinics, though it may also be used in hospital settings for admitted patients. This code frequently appears on EOB statements for patients with documented Lyme disease who receive treatment for related neurological symptoms.",
