    "whoUses": "Neurologists, infectious disease specialists, and hospitalists typically diagnose and manage vCJD, usually in hospital or specialized neurology clinic settings. This code appears on EOB statements for patients with confirmed or suspected vCJD, though cases are extremely rare in most developed countries due to beef safety regulations implemented in the 1990s.",
