    "whoUses": "Infectious disease specialists, emergency medicine physicians, and primary care doctors use this code when diagnosing patients with arthropod-borne viral infections that don't have a more specific diagnosis. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients evaluated in urgent care or hospital settings during insect-borne illness seasons, particularly in tropical or subtropical regions.",
